LongGammaWrapperOpen
├── when a user deposits upfront collateral and the wrapper opens a long
│   ├── it deposits collateral to the trackers as the wrapper so the wrapper owns the shares
│   ├── it leaves the user holding zero collateral shares
│   ├── it mints a long gamma position with isLong one against the seeded seller short
│   ├── it reports numberOfLegs greater than zero for the wrapper
│   ├── it reads back a single position balance with positionSize greater than zero
│   └── it transitions state from Uninitialized to Open and stores the user and tokenId
└── when deposit is called a second time after the position is open
    └── it reverts WrongState because the wrapper is one shot
